### Variabel (Biar gampang ganti-ganti)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = isi_token_jwt_disini

### 1. Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "galih",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "galih",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get All Tasks (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/getTasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Delete Task (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/69f095286f4e1a26fbaf7c4a
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}